## Royalties distribution

### Writer
- First sell: 85%
- Other trades and rental: 10%

### Owner
- First sell: 0%
- Other trades: 80%
- rental: 75%

### Corbind
- First sell: 15%
- Other trades: 10%
- rental: 15%